2. **App.tsx onResize debounce**:
   - 기존:
     ```ts
     onResize={(size) => {
       if (size >= minSize) {
         persistWorkspacePanelState({ size });
         setWorkspacePanelState({ size });
       }
     }}
     ```
   - 수정 옵션 A(rAF debounce):
     ```ts
     const pendingRef = useRef<number | null>(null);
     const lastSizeRef = useRef<number>(size);
     onResize={(size) => {
       lastSizeRef.current = size;
       if (pendingRef.current != null) return;
       pendingRef.current = requestAnimationFrame(() => {
         pendingRef.current = null;
         const latest = lastSizeRef.current;
         if (latest >= minSize) {
           persistWorkspacePanelState({ size: latest });
           setWorkspacePanelState({ size: latest });
         }
       });
     }}
     ```
   - 옵션 B(timeout 16ms debounce): 유사 효과, rAF보다 단순
   - 권장: 옵션 A. React concurrent 렌더와 정합
